Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Hanging in there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:11.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we may be in over our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:21.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you could use a hand, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:24.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Fighting requires rationality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:29.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Fighting single-handedly against countless foes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:33.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Such foolishness will only wear you out\Nbefore you're beaten senseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:38.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,And fighting also requires\Na sense of aesthetic beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:41.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Major Armstrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:50.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,A beautiful physique begets beautiful skills,\Nand beautiful skills beget beautiful power!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:55.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Behold! The artistic alchemy that is\Nthe Armstrong tradition!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:02.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Come on, this isn't your show.\NWould you stop screwing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Just give them the message, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:09.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Hi, Lieutenant Hawkeye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:14.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You mean you could tell...\Nthat I'm me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:20.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Edward, we've got trouble.\NArmony's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:22.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,What?! Who's got her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:26.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,The professor's assistant, Greta.\NThey're probably still in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:29.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Just leave this place to us.\NGo rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,She's counting on both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:33.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:35.00,Helvetica,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
